  "text": "VSV titre was determined by plaque assay on Vero monolayer cells as previously described. [CITATION_1] Briefly, 10-fold serially-diluted viruscontaining supernatant was added into Vero cells and incubated for 2 hours at 37°C. Then, DMEM containing 2% FBS and 1% methylcellulose (Sigma) was added after removing the supernatant. Plaques were counted at day 3 post-infection.",
